|year=c. 1601–1602
|first=William
|last=Shakespeare
|authorlink=William Shakespeare
|title={{w|Twelfth Night}}
|section=act 1, scene 3
|lines=53–54
|passage=You mistake, knight. ‘'''Accost'''’ is front / her, board her, woo her, assail her.
}}
